name: Corneo's Ball Gag TI Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding to add a ball gag to characters, usually a red one.

This is my last upload, at least for a while. Retire at the top of your game, they say, and now I've hit #1 rank on here and done most of the embeds I wanted to do, I'm at a tipping point from this going from a fun hobby to another chore job. So I'm heading in to semi-retirement and getting back to a big personal project that started me off down this path in the first place. Apologies if your request wasn't popular enough to have been high enough of the list to get made, but I'm seeing more and more people post excellent TIs and other stuff on here now. If I make anything for personal use that's good, I'll still post it here, but I'm closing requests and other work.

Example images produced with my (new) Shinra26 Mix https://civitai.com/models/5943/corneos-shinra26-mix (It's a decent alternative to 7th Heaven).

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
